JOHANNESBURG – Five children have died after a high-mast light ring fell on them in Soshanguve, North of Pretoria. City of Tshwane officials believe the light post may have been tampered with by cable thieves. READ: Police not ruling out muti-killing after 4 children die The incident occurred when the children, aged between 5 and 12, were playing around it. Four of them died on the scene and the fifth died in hospital. Police are investigating eNCA